Heather Thomson SCHINDLER, et al., Respondents,
v.
Eric ROTHFELD, et al., Appellants, Times Three Clothier, LLC, Nominal Defendant. 2018-156 Court of Appeals of New York. April 3, 2018

(And Another Action.)
